- Just calm down.

17:06.592 --> 17:07.569
What's wrong with you?

17:07.894 --> 17:08.804
I'm going to the Embassy.

17:08.961 --> 17:10.804
We'll get out of Kuwait
once even/thing's arranged.

17:10.963 --> 17:12.101
Okay. Relax now.

17:35.188 --> 17:36.326
Nair, don't be scared.

