in Arabic language.

17:58.077 --> 18:01.183
Nair please sit in the car.

18:02.415 --> 18:03.416
Nair!

18:46.726 --> 18:48.763
Get in!

18:54.700 --> 18:56.179
Play the music.

18:57.770 --> 19:00.683
What's that shining in your hand?
Give it to us.

19:00.873 --> 19:02.944
Good, good!

19:28.868 --> 19:30.040
Come on, move.

19:34.106 --> 19:36.518
'You must be really happy today'.

19:40.613 --> 19:41.887
Amitabh Bachchan...?

19:42.848 --> 19:43.826
Deewar...?

19:44.984 --> 19:47.726
Mr. Ranjit, yes or no?

19:56.529 --> 19:59.237
If I hadn't passed through
that checkpoint today...

19:59.899 --> 20:02.971
then you wouldn't be still alive,
Mr. Ranjit.

20:04.103 --> 20:05.241
Let me guess...

20:07.773 --> 20:11.118
You didn't recognise me.

20:17.016 --> 20:19.758
A year ago... you came to Baghdad...

20:20.119 --> 20:24.033
with your wife Amrita
and daughter Simran...

20:24.090 --> 20:25.330
for a Fundraiser.

20:25.691 --> 20:29.366
And by the grace of Allah...
who was your security in-charge?

20:32.832 --> 20:35.108
I was with you for two days...

20:35.801 --> 20:38.611
yet you don't recognise me.

20:40.039 --> 20:43.179
I am kind of hum, Mr. Katiyal.

20:44.610 --> 20:47.853
- I remember...
- No! You don't!

20:50.616 --> 20:55.588
Successful people...
should only remember important people.

20:55.654 --> 20:59.363
And now... suddenly...
I am someone important.

21:00.126 --> 21:04.802
Mr. Khallaf Bin Zayed.
Iraqi Republican Army.

21:04.964 --> 21:07.706
- At your service.
- Thank you.

21:08.067 --> 21:10.013
I'll give you plenty
of oppurtunities...

21:10.069 --> 21:12.106
to express your gratitude.

21:12.238 --> 21:13.615
Like I gave him.

21:18.044 --> 21:19.045
Fawad?

21:19.278 --> 21:20.757
<i>Fawad Al Sawed.</i>

21:20.913 --> 21:22.915
Your business partner.

21:23.382 --> 21:26.693
Al An Hazir Iraq, Mr. Katiyal.

21:26.886 --> 21:28.194
Now this is Iraq.

21:28.387 --> 21:30.424
And people like you...

21:30.890 --> 21:34.133
will help us keep it that way.

21:35.261 --> 21:37.969
I'm taking another step towards that.

21:39.131 --> 21:41.236
A small gift.

21:41.634 --> 21:42.635
This sticker.

21:43.302 --> 21:45.714
Put it on the windshield of your car.

21:45.905 --> 21:47.384
It'll be helpful at checkpoints.

21:47.740 --> 21:51.187
Otherwise... we could
be meeting every day.

21:55.414 --> 21:58.088
We're friends now, Mr. Ranjit.

21:58.784 --> 22:00.422
If you ever need anything...

22:00.753 --> 22:03.893
don't hesitate.

22:04.089 --> 22:07.093
In return... l'm sure
you too honor this friendship.

22:07.726 --> 22:09.034
You can go.

22:26.045 --> 22:27.456
Mr.Saini.

22:27.680 --> 22:31.355
Mr. Katiyal, over here.

22:31.684 --> 22:32.992
Thank God you saw me.

22:36.255 --> 22:37.256
It's okay.

22:38.023 --> 22:38.831
Brij!

22:38.958 --> 22:41.234
Brij! What the hell is happening?

22:41.460 --> 22:42.905
What happened? Calm down.

22:42.962 --> 22:46.876
