23:25.471 --> 23:26.575
No one can come in.

23:26.639 --> 23:27.982
And there's no question of leaving.

23:28.073 --> 23:29.711
And the Indian Government?

23:29.875 --> 23:31.183
As usual, must be watching the show.

23:31.477 --> 23:32.421
Your Kuwaiti government...

23:32.478 --> 23:33.548
didn't even wait
for the show to start.

23:33.679 --> 23:34.783
They fled.

23:35.014 --> 23:37.517
Policy decisions
are not made in hours.

23:38.217 --> 23:40.060
