right in front of my eyes.

29:50.789 --> 29:53.133
Little kids are walking
around with guns.

29:54.693 --> 29:56.866
Fawad Al Sayyed was
hanging off a crane.

29:56.995 --> 29:59.805
- Oh <i>my...</i>
- So what is Ranjit Katiyal worth?

30:01.700 --> 30:05.477
