30:26.792 --> 30:27.702
Mother.

32:10.829 --> 32:13.366
Mr. Ranjit, why are you standing?

32:13.432 --> 32:15.105
- Please sit.
- Thank you.

32:15.233 --> 32:16.371
Not here.

32:18.236 --> 32:19.271
Here.

32:28.313 --> 32:31.988
There's a price to everything,
Mr. Ranjit.

32:32.918 --> 32:34.761
I am ready to pay.

32:35.187 --> 32:38.862
